    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2019 premium SUV is the ideal choice for a buyer seeking a reliable, high-performing vehicle without the new-car price tag. The exterior retains a deep, glossy metallic finish, showing only very minor stone chips consistent with light highway use. Inside, the smoke-free cabin is exceptionally clean; the leather upholstery is supple and free of cracks, while the dual-zone climate control and premium sound system operate perfectly. Mechanically, this vehicle excels. It comes with a complete, documented service history, having recently passed a comprehensive inspection and oil service. The tires have significant tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It drives smoothly with no rattles or hesitations, offering a turn-key experience for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
